ğŸ“Š Project Motivation

Aviation engines undergo high thermal and mechanical stress. Manually scheduled maintenance is often:

Costly

Inefficient

Reactive instead of preventive

This project enables predictive maintenance, allowing airlines / MRO teams to:

Estimate engine wear

Replace parts at the correct time

Reduce downtime

Improve fleet safety

